import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Scrabble Words from Hindu Mythology — Sacred Terms That Score"
  description="Hindu mythology words valid in Scrabble with full scoring. CHAKRA (15pts), DHARMA (12pts), KARMA (11pts). Ancient Sanskrit-origin vocabulary for competitive Scrabble."
  keywords="scrabble hindu mythology words, karma scrabble points, chakra scrabble, dharma scrabble, sanskrit words scrabble, hindu words valid scrabble"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article","headline":"Scrabble Words from Hindu Mythology — Sacred Terms That Score","description":"Hindu mythology words valid in Scrabble with full scoring. CHAKRA (15pts), DHARMA (12pts), KARMA (11pts).","datePublished":"2026-07-01","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com","url":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com"},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/scrabble-words-from-mythology-hindu"}})} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is KARMA a valid Scrabble word?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes! KARMA scores 11 points (K=5, A=1, R=1, M=3, A=1). It means the cosmic principle of cause and effect. Valid in both TWL and SOWPODS dictionaries."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you play CHAKRA in Scrabble?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. CHAKRA scores 15 points (C=3, H=4, A=1, K=5, R=1, A=1). It refers to energy centres in Hindu philosophy. The K=5 and H=4 combination makes it a strong 6-letter play."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is DHARMA valid in Scrabble?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes! DHARMA scores 12 points (D=2, H=4, A=1, R=1, M=3, A=1). It means cosmic law or righteous duty. Valid in SOWPODS. The H=4 and M=3 give it solid scoring."}}]})} />
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1"><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a><span class="mx-1">›</span><span class="text-gray-300">Word Lists</span></nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words from Hindu Mythology — Sacred Terms That Score</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400"><time datetime="2026-07-01">July 1, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a></div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Hindu mythology has gifted English with dozens of Sanskrit-origin words — and many are valid in competitive Scrabble. These ancient terms carry H, K, and M tiles that deliver consistent scoring power from your rack.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">15 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">CHAKRA</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">12 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">DHARMA</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">11 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">KARMA</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">9 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">MANTRA</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top-Scoring Hindu Mythology Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Top Scorer</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">CHAKRA — 15 Points</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">C=3, H=4, A=1, K=5, R=1, A=1 · 6 letters</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">An energy centre in Hindu and Buddhist traditions. CHAKRA combines three premium consonants — C=3, H=4, K=5 — for 15 points from just 6 tiles. Pluralises easily to CHAKRAS.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🙏 DHARMA</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">12 pts · D=2, H=4, A=1, R=1, M=3, A=1 · Cosmic law</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">☸️ KARMA</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">11 pts · K=5, A=1, R=1, M=3, A=1 · Cause and effect</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🕉️ MANTRA</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">8 pts · M=3, A=1, N=1, T=1, R=1, A=1 · Sacred chant</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🧘 YOGA</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">8 pts · Y=4, O=1, G=2, A=1 · Spiritual practice</p></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">More Sanskrit-Origin Words</h2>
      <p>Many everyday English words trace back to Hindu traditions and score well:</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">AVATAR</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">9pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">NIRVANA</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">10pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">GURU</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">5pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">PUNDIT</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">9pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">TANTRA</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">6pts</span></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy for Hindu Mythology Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">CHAKRA is your K-tile play:</span> With K=5 plus C=3 and H=4, CHAKRA delivers 15 points from 6 tiles. Hook it to CHAKRAS for an extra S point and rack clearance.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">KARMA is always available:</span> K, A, R, M, A are common draws. At 11 points for 5 tiles, KARMA has excellent points-per-tile efficiency (2.2 per tile).</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">NIRVANA is a 7-letter bingo:</span> At 10 base points + 50 bonus = 60 total, NIRVANA uses all common tiles. Keep N, I, R, V together when you see A, N, A available.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Key Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Hindu mythology words are <span class="text-white font-medium">K-tile and H-tile naturals</span>. CHAKRA, KARMA, and DHARMA all use K=5 or H=4 to punch above their length. These are words most opponents won't think of playing.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-mythology-japanese/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Mythology Japanese</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-mythology-greek/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Greek Mythology</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-mythology-norse/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Norse Mythology</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-yoga/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Yoga</span></a>
        </div>
